<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<aiml>
    <category>
        <pattern>*</pattern>
        <template>
            I'm not sure how to respond to that. My name is Careerbot and I can to help you find what computer 
            science job is right for you. 
            <br/>
            <b>Please say "hello" to me and we can get started looking for your new career!</b>
        </template>
    </category>
    <category>
        <pattern>HELLO ^</pattern>
        <template>
            Hello! My name is Careerbot and I'm here to help you find what computer science job is right for you!
            <br/>
            I'm going to ask you a few questions to see what job would suit your background 
            and preferences. 
            <br/>
            Please answer the questions the best you can so I can give you the most awesome information! 
            With all that said, let's get started!
            <br/>
            <b>What is your <set name="topic">favorite course</set> from your college journey?</b>
        </template>
    </category>
    <topic name="favorite course">
        <category>
            <pattern>^ <set>mathclasses</set> ^</pattern>
            <template>
                I see you like math! <star index="2"/> in particular can be really useful for a number of jobs.
                <br/>
                <b>What class did you find to be your <set name="topic">least favorite</set> while you were taking it?</b>
            </template>
        </category>
        <category>
            <pattern>^ <set>networkclasses</set> ^</pattern>
            <template>
                I see you like networking! <star index="2"/> in particular can be really useful for a number of jobs.
                <br/>
                <b>What class did you find to be your <set name="topic">least favorite</set> while you were taking it?</b>
            </template>
        </category>
        <category>
            <pattern>^ <set>infosecclasses</set> ^</pattern>
            <template>
                I see you like security! <star index="2"/> in particular can be really useful for a number of jobs.
                <br/>
                <b>What class did you find to be your <set name="topic">least favorite</set> while you were taking it?</b>
            </template>
        </category>
        <category>
            <pattern>^ <set>interactiveclasses</set> ^</pattern>
            <template>
                I see you like something more interactive and with variety! <star index="2"/> in particular can be really useful for a number of jobs.
                <br/>
                <b>What class did you find to be your <set name="topic">least favorite</set> while you were taking it?</b>
            </template>
        </category>
        <category>
            <pattern>^ <set>programmingclasses</set> ^</pattern>
            <template>
                I see you like programming! <star index="2"/> in particular can be really useful for a number of jobs.
                <br/>
