            </template>
        </category>
        <category>
            <pattern>*</pattern>
            <template>
                Wow I haven't heard of that before! Sounds like you've had an exciting Computer Science career!
                <br/>
                <b>What class did you find to be your <set name="topic">least favorite</set> while you were taking it?</b>
            </template>
        </category>
    </topic>
    <topic name="least favorite">
        <category>
            <pattern>^ <set>mathclasses</set> ^</pattern>
            <template>
                I can understand that! Math classes like <star index="2"/> can be offputting for a number of reasons. I'm glad you go through it though!
                <br/>
                <b>Now that I got what your favorites are, what are some <set name="topic">hobbies</set> you have?</b>
            </template>
        </category>
        <category>
            <pattern>^ <set>networkclasses</set> ^</pattern>
            <template>
                I can understand that! Network classes like <star index="2"/> can be offputting for a number of reasons. I'm glad you go through it though!
                <br/>
