            </template>
        </category>
        <category>
            <pattern>*</pattern>
            <template>
                Even though that class don't ring a bell for me, It still sounds like a hassel to deal with!
                <br/>
                <b>Now that I got what your favorites are, what are some <set name="topic">hobbies</set> you have?</b>
            </template>
        </category>
    </topic>
    <topic name="hobbies">
    </topic>
    <category>
        <pattern>HI ^</pattern>
        <template><srai>HELLO *</srai></template>
    </category>
    <category>
        <pattern># <set>positivebeforenoun</set> ^ MATH ^</pattern>
        <template>I'm glad you <star index="2"/> math! It's fantastic!</template>
    </category>
    <category>
        <pattern># MATH ^ <set>positiveafternoun</set> ^</pattern>
        <template>I'm glad you think math <person><star index="2"/></person> <star index="3"/>! It is really great!</template>
    </category>
    <category>
        <pattern>^ I * ^ MATH ^</pattern>
        <template>I'm sorry to hear you <star index="2"/> math! It's fantastic!</template>
    </category>
</aiml>
